    <item>
      <title>诺和诺德首席执行官称已做好应对特朗普关税威胁的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/novo-nordisk-is-prepared-for-trump-s-tariff-threat-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[目前，哥本哈根和华盛顿之间的紧张局势正在升温，丹麦制药商诺和诺德公司的首席执行官表示，该公司已做好应对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能征收的关税的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/novo-nordisk-is-prepared-for-trump-s-tariff-threat-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普接管加沙的想法得到以色列支持，阿拉伯人反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-idea-for-us-takeover-of-gaza-stokes-middle-east-divisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的减少加沙人口并接管加沙的想法在以色列受到广泛欢迎，官员们称赞这一意外提议是加强与哈马斯战争后安全的一种手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-idea-for-us-takeover-of-gaza-stokes-middle-east-divisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国邮政局撤销暂停向中国发货的决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政局表示，将接受来自中国和香港邮政的“所有国际入境邮件和包裹”，撤回了几个小时前宣布的暂停部分海外货运的公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在解决医疗保险僵局方面取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/south-africa-signals-breakthrough-in-health-insurance-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府表示，其在解决新国家医疗保险计划僵局方面正在取得进展，批评人士称该计划将侵犯患者和医护人员的权利，并使私营部门受到边缘化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/south-africa-signals-breakthrough-in-health-insurance-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 10:47:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>历史性减税措施出台后莫迪面临重大选举考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/modi-faces-first-major-electoral-test-after-historic-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度首都的选民于周三参加了投票，这对总理纳伦德拉·莫迪来说是一次至关重要的考验，十多年来，他的政党一直未能从一个规模虽小但实力强大的竞争对手手中夺取德里的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/modi-faces-first-major-electoral-test-after-historic-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
